aa456ace-e727-4b0f-9e65-78ae64215503.title: Madame Caldarium
aa456ace-e727-4b0f-9e65-78ae64215503.text:
You guess? The sun is shining, the sea breeze is salty,
what's not to enjoy?

d4bc31fd-c9e9-489a-b0bc-e0f77d6c0b70.title: <player>
d4bc31fd-c9e9-489a-b0bc-e0f77d6c0b70.text:
I don't know... The sand? It's coarse and rough and
irritating, and it gets everywhere.

8606953e-ad17-47ef-b657-5e546c6b7477.title: Madame Caldarium
8606953e-ad17-47ef-b657-5e546c6b7477.text:
Hmm, well my spa isn't quite ready yet, but when it is,
I'm sure that'll solve all of your sand related issues!

c9fd7fa4-d8a0-4170-9df2-543d579a53ab.title: Madame Caldarium
c9fd7fa4-d8a0-4170-9df2-543d579a53ab.text:
I am Madame Caldarium! A pirate's life was for me, but
lately I've been looking to expand my business, I'm
getting old, ya see.

756f71f9-bcb4-4320-977e-581c31f61bb6.title: <player>
756f71f9-bcb4-4320-977e-581c31f61bb6.text:
A spa business? Do you really think these Corsairs are
the washing type?

8159a9d8-4020-4533-b6b1-4ae3e19b7af9.title: Madame Caldarium
8159a9d8-4020-4533-b6b1-4ae3e19b7af9.text: Ha! That's what the Rum is for!

2e6c101e-6080-4000-baa4-a056088e41a2.title: Madame Caldarium
2e6c101e-6080-4000-baa4-a056088e41a2.text:
I'm more concerned of their laziness, 'Can't work
today Madame, I'm cursed!'. Bunch of idiots, the lot of
'em.

86bed399-4962-48ce-8775-41bd962c705b.title: <player>
86bed399-4962-48ce-8775-41bd962c705b.text:
Surely you never expected this lot to be any different...
They're either stealing, killing or both!

4a85696f-4f58-492e-88db-ac7fbf14eeb2.title: Madame Caldarium
4a85696f-4f58-492e-88db-ac7fbf14eeb2.text:
Yes... I have plans adventurer, the local cave dwelling
population are... Let's say, sorting something out.

fc56e666-36b2-4a7f-a3f2-744d6a7d56f0.title: <player>
fc56e666-36b2-4a7f-a3f2-744d6a7d56f0.text:
Interesting, I'm sure that'll be an entertaining turn of
events.
